urls.title: Warren to feds: Why did you take Massachusetts’ medical supplies? - The Boston Globe
urls.description: Senator Elizabeth Warren is pressing federal officials for answers on why they seized at least two of Massachusetts’ recent orders for protective equipment.

text: The Trump administration has failed to provide states with the necessary resources and medical supplies to fight this pandemic. Now they're outbidding the states and seizing our orders. I'm demanding answers. https://t.co/tt2FLB0icM
